text: Ærest æt gorgrafes slæde on ðæt crundel.
Of ðam crundelle on læces ford, on ðone mor.
Of ðane forda on ceobban hangran.
Of ðan hangran on ðæt wæterslæd.
Of ðan wæterslæde on sceobban oran wylle.
Of sceobban oran wylle on wrohthangran.
Of wrohthangran on cybban stan.
Of ðan stane on ðone hrycgweg.
Andlang weges on Colmenoran.
Of Colmenoran on wændles cumb.
Of ðan cumbe on ðone swanweg.
Of ðan wege on riscleahe ufewearde.
Of riscleahe on ðone rugan weg.
Of ðam wege on ðone lampyt.
Of ðam pytte on ðæs cumbes heafod.
Of ðæs cumbes heafde on ðone portweg, oð ðone greatan þorn.
Of ðan þorne on foxhola cumbe ofeweardne.
Of ðan cumbe to blacan graue, ofeweardan on ða dic.
Andlang dic to heorthamme.
Of heorthamme to Wudaforda.
Of Wudaforda on Pottenes treow.
Of ðan treowe andlang gemæres on ðone mor.
Ðæt up andlang broces on cealdan wyl.
Of cealdan wylle to ðære þornrawe.
Of ðære þornrawe ðæt eft in on gorgrafes slæd.
